-- GCC May Deposit $5 Billion in Yemen to Back Riyal, Asharq Says
-- B y   N a y l a   R a z z o u k
-- 2012-02-28T08:54:35Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-28/gcc-may-deposit-5-billion-in-yemen-to-back-riyal-asharq-says.html
The six-nation Gulf Cooperation
Council may deposit $5 billion in  Yemen ’s central bank to back
the national currency, according to Asharq Al-Awsat.  Yemen’s new president, Abdurabuh Mansur Hadi, discussed
details of the procedure during a meeting with GCC Secretary-
General Abdel Latif al Zayyani, the newspaper reported without
saying where it got the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Nayla Razzouk in Dubai at 
 nrazzouk2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew J. Barden at 
 barden@bloomberg.net  